name: Anaerobic Capacity into Sweetspot #1
description:
Sweetspot intervals are generally considered comfortable efforts, completed over longer durations. 



We finish the session with a steady 5min Sweetspot interval in today's workout. 



However, with the effort preceded by a series of 1min Anaerobic Capacity efforts, it may not be as comfortable as expected!
            


            This workout is also available as Video workout by a MyWhoosh coach Lisa Hermansson
